      "name": "Mesh convergence GCI study — all five operating points",
      "description": "Richardson extrapolation-based GCI computed on three systematically refined meshes (1.2M, 4.8M, 19.2M cells). GCI values: 1.8% at 2.5 L/min, 2.1% at 3.5 L/min, 2.6% at 4.5 L/min, 2.3% at 5.5 L/min, 1.9% at 6.5 L/min. All below the 3% threshold.",
